{
  "stem": "22750.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the feeling from us-- and I came right over [INAUDIBLE], we came on orders [? for us. ?] And I came back to the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And at that time, I took my wife with my kid and the other-- if you ask me, it came to this subject-- the other, from my little city, the Judenrat, Shlomo Sherman-- you have the name-- came to me and says, George.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "At that time, they didn't call me George.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But I say George.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We have a befiehl.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Befiehl means, like, order from a big officer from the SS to give him a big forecoat for winter.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They didn't call it a coat, but I say a coat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And fore because they are this-- to cover up when they go on a sled in wintertime.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And I was nervous already because I just came in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And his name was Shlomo.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I mentioned the name there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And I told him, Shlomo, I'm not going anymore to do this.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "It's danger from us, from nervousness.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And not the mind was, in the that time, you can't even think, not in normal.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the answer was-- he was, what do you say?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, a panic-- there will be a panic in the-- I say, that's what it is.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that's all.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he went out.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And what he told me in that time, I was one of the only Jews who survived.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And this is something.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 10 SECONDS] [SOBBING] I mention the name, not because I wanted-- what I chose at that time, as he's a better Jew with a better feeling.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He [INAUDIBLE] survived.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That's what the answer to me was.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was one of the only Jews to survive.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It was, well, we were told the Jews were with me.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
